               feloniously stealing on the 19th of March, two pewter pots, value 18 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820410-48-victim608" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Eldridge
                  <interp inst="t17820410-48-victim608" type="surname" value="Eldridge"></interp>
